      "rationale": "The nonlinear implicit FEA formulation with frictional contact and bilinear isotropic hardening material model was selected based on prior literature. Model form errors assessed via E/uval: 0.87 (stiffness), 1.31 (yield force), 1.54 (force at 40 mm). All below 1.96 threshold."
