      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties (Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus, yield strength, tangent modulus) and geometric dimensions sourced from traceable measurements; uncertainty quantified via Latin Hypercube Sampling (N=200).",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V material properties obtained from tensile coupon testing (N=5) of the same material lot as test constructs. Geometric dimensions measured via CMM on three representative screws. LHS uncertainty propagation (N=200 samples) yielded combined model input uncertainty of 3.1% for stiffness QoI."
