      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span at least two loading configurations or environmental conditions representative of the COU; inter-laboratory reproducibility demonstrated.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 configuration (compression-bending only) at room temperature. Inter-laboratory reproducibility confirmed (CV < 5% across labs). However, only one test condition was evaluated, limiting coverage to Gradation 2. This shortfall is accepted given that compression-bending is the dominant loading mode for this COU and additional test conditions would not materially change the credibility conclusion."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
