      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA model inputs (geometry, material properties, boundary conditions) demonstrably equivalent to experimental test article and setup; differences quantified and propagated into uncertainty budget.",
      "rationale": "FEA model geometry derived from CAD nominal with measured deviations applied. Boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture kinematics. Friction coefficients measured via dedicated tribology testing. Remaining equivalency gaps (e.g., residual stresses from manufacturing) assessed as negligible contributors to QoI uncertainty."
    },
