      "rationale": "Construct stiffness relates to load-sharing with the spine; yield force and force at 40 mm correspond to implant survival under worst-case physiological loading. All three QoIs are explicitly required by FDA guidance for pedicle screw 510(k) submissions and are directly traceable to design input requirements."
