    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3; this shortfall is accepted because compression-bending is the sole dominant loading mode in the COU and inter-laboratory reproducibility was demonstrated. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support regulatory use of the FEA framework for the non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending COU. Package hash recorded; signature workflow is pending and will be applied prior to submission.",
